divs: sighting detailsmy last ufo. i went outside to my back garden as i heard my dog barking. told him to calm down and to come in but he was looking up when he was barking. i looked and saw a tree but as i looked more closely to my dogs eyes, i noticed he was looking up in the sky and that is when i saw it. it was bright, started off flashing different colours and must of been there for at 3 minutes. my feelings at the time was that it could be a plane or helicopter but have seen then before in the dark and this was no plane or helicopter i had seen before. it went from flashing green to yellow to blue. then there was a flash and it had just disappeared. have seen more in the last few years and have took some photos. my name is (*wit's name deleted--cms\sg)by the way and i'm a beginner ufologist and my email is *(wit's email address deleted--cms\sg) in case anybody wants to talk about it.
